<div class="introduction">
  <h1>Hi, my name is Christian</h1>
  <p>Glad you're here! At this point you have 3 options:</p>
  {{#link-to 'resume' class="btn"}}Read all about me!{{/link-to}}
  <a class="btn">Get in touch</a>
  {{#unless bounce}}
    <a class="btn" {{action toggleProperty 'bounce'}}>Bounce</a>
  {{else}}
    <a class="btn" {{action bounceForReal}}>Bounce (for real)</a>
  {{/unless}}
  {{#if bounce}}
    <p>Come on, you know how this works, here are some ideas to get you started:
      <ul>
        <li>Just close the tab, with your mouse</li>
        <li>Use cmd &#8984; + W</li>
        <li>Throw your Mac out of the window...</li>
      </ul>
      Or, you know, click bounce again, let me help you out!
    </p>
  {{/if}}
</div>
